bot diddley – a twitter and blues bot for keeping track of twitter followers.

bot diddley will regularly check your list of followers on twitter and notify
you when someone follows or – more importantly – unfollows you.


setting things up is easy:

0> create a twitter account for your bot => https://twitter.com/signup
0.5> set the account to private if you wish to be private about your followers
1> you need an amazon web services account
2> install the yaml, json and s3 gems
3> edit config/botdiddley.yml.template, save as config/botdiddley.yml
4> go: ruby botdiddley.rb
